ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, I would recommend this course. This is the most difficult language that I have studied, but the proficiency of the professor makes it an attainable language.
I would describe it as a course that is challenging but taught be an instructor who cares and keeps students interested.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I want to move to kenya and work there one day so understanding the language and who to speak in an educated manner is very helpful. No, dissertation/research applicable to me.
This class is an essential part of my studies.
